310
00:22:10,750 --> 00:22:12,291
Tudo certo, você pode ir.

311
00:22:12,375 --> 00:22:14,125
[respiram aliviados]

312
00:22:15,583 --> 00:22:17,583
[motor liga]

313
00:22:17,666 --> 00:22:19,458
[música alegre suave]

314
00:22:19,541 --> 00:22:21,000
